        <p>Step 2: Place the resources.assets file in the following directory: ..\steamapps\common\Motorsport Manager\MM_Data</p>
        <p>Step 3: Place the Assembly-CSharp.dll and Assembly-CSharp-firstpass.dll in the following directory: ..\steamapps\common\Motorsport Manager\MM_Data\Managed</p>
        <p>Step 4: Subscribe to the Rebirth: Logo Pack on Steam: <a target='_blank' href='https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1188384463'>Rebirth: Logo Pack</a></p>
        <p>Step 5: Start the game, go to 'Steam Workshop' on the main menu screen, then select 'Assets' on the left, and filter by subscribed mods and activate the Logo Pack. If you do not do this, you will end up with white squares where logos should be.</p>
        <p>Step 6: Start a new save, go to any of the GT or single seaster series - if you have 12 teams to choose from and you don't recognise 2 of them, the mod is installed and working.</p>
